title: Transfer testnet NFTs on mainnet launch
body:
We should encourage people to test new releases of CoinClicker pre initial mainnet launch. 

To achieve this, and have full test coverage including the frequent pulling of rugs, I propose that NFTs (rugs) acquired on the Rinkeby testnet should be transferred to their respective owners upon mainnet launch. 

NFT rewards can be seen as supplement to the current CCGT rewards -- which are also transferred upon mainnet launch.
author: 0x4b8E01489EA94ac9dc660848A484C7Edb9cE5ec8
